<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She has turned her stripes as a world famous fashion model.</p>

<p>And Arizona Muse used the red carpet as her runway on Saturday evening, as she arrived at the Marx premiere during the 77th Venice Film Festival.</p>

<p>The British-American star, 31, looked breathtaking in a stunning red gown, which boasted a deeply plunging neckline complete with ruffled detailing.</p>

<p>Lady in red! Arizona Muse used the red carpet as her runway on Saturday evening, as she arrived at the Marx premiere during the 77th Venice Film Festival</p>

<p>Arizona's gown was cinched around her svelte waist and featured a full skirt which cascaded down to the carpet, as she strutted her way into the event.</p>

<p>The Vogue Cover girl added sparkle to her look with a dazzling diamond necklace and a pair of simple hoop earrings.</p>

<p>She let her natural beauty shine through as she sported a natural pallet of make-up, while wearing her highlighted locks in a loose bouncy style. </p>

<p>Stunning: The British-American star, 31, looked breathtaking in a stunning red gown, which boasted a deeply plunging neckline complete with ruffled detailing</p>

<p>Arizona welcomed her first child Nikko, 10, with fashion stylist and former flame Manuel Quintana when she was 20.</p>

<p>Speaking to Town and Country magazine, the beauty reflected on being a young parent.</p>

<p>She said: 'I don’t know what it’s like to be a 20-year-old who didn’t have a child. I loved having Nikko.</p>

<p>Red carpet ready: Arizona's gown was cinched around her svelte waist and featured a full skirt which cascaded down to the carpet, as she strutted her way into the event</p>

<p>'He was like a doll. I was a child myself and it was an "ignorance is bliss" situation.'</p>

<p>Arizona candidly admitted her reasoning for marriage being particularly meaningful to her, given that Nikko 'doesn't have a relationship' with her ex-fiancé Manuel.</p>

<p>She said: 'It meant a lot to me to get married. Especially because I already had a child who doesn’t have a relationship with his dad.'</p>

<p>Touching on how she burnt herself out by working and parenting in the early days, she told: 'By the time Nikko was three, I was totally exhausted.'</p>

<p>Details: The Vogue Cover girl added sparkle to her look with a dazzling diamond necklace and a pair of simple hoop earrings</p>

<p>Arizona battled on because she feared that if she took time off her career would disappear - which caused her massive amounts of stress that she 'was under, every single day, for years'.</p>

<p>She added: 'I probably needed to take some time off, but I was stuck in this fear cycle.</p>

<p>Arizona announced the arrival of her baby daughter by sharing an adorable snap of her laying alongside the newborn in November 2018.</p>

